  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across five flow-speed combinations. Thirteen credibility factors were assessed; the majority achieved required levels. Decision recorded as Accepted based on overall engineering judgment that residual gaps are manageable. Note: two factors carry achievedLevel below requiredLevel, representing the targeted W-AR-02 rebutting defeater.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-claim",
